{"tid":1139350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消委會點名譴責4間健身中心　腦退化女子失175萬元","createTime":"2019-05-05T07:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T12:51:46.000Z","uid":60344,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1d98ab456f592317845b709611fb7efad8d42ffa","tid":1139350,"uid":60344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T07:54:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1451844-20190408.htm?archive_date=2019-04-08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1451844-20190408.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2019-04-08&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2y1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=54b97d2c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1451844-20190408.htm%3Farchive_date%3D2019-04-08&h=6f0ec26a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1451844-20190408.htm?archive_date=2019-04-08</a><br />\n<br />\n消委會點名譴責4間健身中心，以年輕人為高壓銷售目標，包括透過恐嚇、強迫購買連鎖店的禮券甚至借貸，來繳付會籍費用，金額最高的個案達175萬元，涉及一名腦退化患者。<br />\n<br />\n消委會發現，有職員以不同方法，了解事主財政狀況，度身訂造會籍，為求「拎到盡」，做人咋舌，非常離譜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲健身佬真係唔驚比雷劈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入條link 聽埋報導，好恐怖，冇人性，專向啲弱勢社群埋手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89fc23d3cad6eb33c0f15a41d51de79bbf8b8044","tid":1139350,"uid":80814,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T08:09:07.000Z","msg":"消委會點名批評嘅旺角健身中心疑改名，唔夠一個月即有受害人出現<br />\n<br />\n健身狗苦主聯盟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1136237\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1136237</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係黃頁search受害人po出嚟嘅電話號碼，出咗一間叫Fitness Express Co Ltd<br />\n<br />\n<i